---
name: agent-loop
description: An agent that uses tools in a loop
model:
  id: gpt-4o
  provider: openai
  apiType: chat
  connection:
    kind: key
    apiKey: ${env:OPENAI_API_KEY:test-key}
inputs:
  - name: question
    kind: string
    default: What is the weather in Seattle and New York?
tools:
  - name: get_weather
    kind: function
    description: Get the current weather for a city
    parameters:
      - name: city
        kind: string
        description: The city name
        required: true
---
system:
You are a helpful assistant. Use the available tools to answer questions.

user:
{{question}}
